OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FEarly cloud will soon break
OL,6,Fup to give a mostly fine day with
OL,7,Fbright or sunny spells. Feeling very
OL,8,Fwarm and muggy. Light winds. Chance of
OL,9,Fisolated thunderstorms by evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMostly
OL,12,Ffine with some sunshine. Turning very
OL,13,Fwarm or locally hot, and feeling humid
OL,14,Ftowards the weekend. Staying mainly
OL,15,Fdry, but with a small chance of
OL,16,Fthunderstorms.
